        <updateDate>2019-09-06T15:59:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Student Loan Bankruptcy Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill allows a student loan to be discharged in bankruptcy, without proving undue hardship, if the loan first became due more than five years before the bankruptcy filing. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
